snippet.title: Exoborne Playtest Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Exoborne Playtest launches on February 12. Be one of the first players to explore Colton County and secure exclusive rewards. Sign-up now! 🎮 https://bit.ly/exoborneplaytest 

Product Rated ESRB M for Mature.

Wishlist on consoles:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10013741 
https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/exoborne/9MWNTZ8G9F57/0010 

Social Links:
https://x.com/exoborne  
https://www.facebook.com/exobornegame  
https://www.instagram.com/exobornegame/  
https://discord.gg/exoborne  
https://www.tiktok.com/@exoborne  
https://www.youtube.com/@Exoborne  

About Exoborne:  
Exoborne is an open-world, tactical extraction shooter set in a world torn apart by extreme forces of nature. Customize powerful exo-rigs to gain strategic advantage in ever-changing weather conditions. Face hostile factions, enemy players, and Mother Nature herself in intense high-stakes sessions. 
Learn more about Exoborne here: http://www.exoborne.com/  

#exoborne #beaforceofnature #playtest #steam
